{
  "source_srt": "how_en.srt",
  "total_segments": 167,
  "segments": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start": "00:00:00,031",
      "end": "00:00:07,021",
      "start_seconds": 0.031,
      "end_seconds": 7.021,
      "text": "Today I'll show you how ChatGPT can be transformed into real learning tools, not just a translator.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_001.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start": "00:00:07,102",
      "end": "00:00:14,533",
      "start_seconds": 7.102,
      "end_seconds": 14.533,
      "text": "Today I won't speak generally, but will use specific prompts and queries that you can also replicate.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_002.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start": "00:00:15,033",
      "end": "00:00:18,799",
      "start_seconds": 15.033,
      "end_seconds": 18.799,
      "text": "For example, today I will show all this at the A1 level.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_003.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start": "00:00:18,779",
      "end": "00:00:20,902",
      "start_seconds": 18.779,
      "end_seconds": 20.902,
      "text": "But this video is not only for beginners.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_004.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start": "00:00:20,922",
      "end": "00:00:25,649",
      "start_seconds": 20.922,
      "end_seconds": 25.649,
      "text": "You will be able to adapt all of this yourself, because we will be building a learning system directly.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_005.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start": "00:00:26,250",
      "end": "00:00:33,580",
      "start_seconds": 26.25,
      "end_seconds": 33.58,
      "text": "You can find ready-made prompts for your level in the pinned comment under the post in my Telegram channel.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_006.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start": "00:00:33,600",
      "end": "00:00:35,102",
      "start_seconds": 33.6,
      "end_seconds": 35.102,
      "text": "And our first step is the base.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_007.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start": "00:00:35,243",
      "end": "00:00:39,268",
      "start_seconds": 35.243,
      "end_seconds": 39.268,
      "text": "You need to know exactly what level of English you have right now.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_008.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start": "00:00:39,449",
      "end": "00:00:43,875",
      "start_seconds": 39.449,
      "end_seconds": 43.875,
      "text": "So it's not okay to write \"I have something between A2 or B1\".",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_009.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start": "00:00:43,855",
      "end": "00:00:49,580",
      "start_seconds": 43.855,
      "end_seconds": 49.58,
      "text": "You need to know your clear level, because then ChatGPT won't be able to create a program specifically for you.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_010.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start": "00:00:49,981",
      "end": "00:00:54,045",
      "start_seconds": 49.981,
      "end_seconds": 54.045,
      "text": "It will either be too easy, or too difficult otherwise.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_011.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start": "00:00:54,065",
      "end": "00:01:01,232",
      "start_seconds": 54.065,
      "end_seconds": 61.232,
      "text": "For this case, I have a ready-made prompt for you, which you can copy and paste into your chat.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_012.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start": "00:01:01,272",
      "end": "00:01:02,133",
      "start_seconds": 61.272,
      "end_seconds": 62.133,
      "text": "I'll read it now.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_013.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start": "00:01:02,673",
      "end": "00:01:04,755",
      "start_seconds": 62.673,
      "end_seconds": 64.755,
      "text": "You are an experienced English teacher.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_014.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start": "00:01:05,095",
      "end": "00:01:07,358",
      "start_seconds": 65.095,
      "end_seconds": 67.358,
      "text": "Help me determine my English level.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_015.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start": "00:01:07,798",
      "end": "00:01:13,103",
      "start_seconds": 67.798,
      "end_seconds": 73.103,
      "text": "Create a series of tasks that test vocabulary, grammar, reading comprehension, speaking.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_016.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start": "00:01:13,083",
      "end": "00:01:15,927",
      "start_seconds": 73.083,
      "end_seconds": 75.927,
      "text": "step-by-step, gradually increasing in difficulty.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_017.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start": "00:01:16,187",
      "end": "00:01:19,511",
      "start_seconds": 76.187,
      "end_seconds": 79.511,
      "text": "After my answers, explain what this means for my level.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_018.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start": "00:01:19,752",
      "end": "00:01:21,053",
      "start_seconds": 79.752,
      "end_seconds": 81.053,
      "text": "And tell me what it is.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_019.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start": "00:01:21,434",
      "end": "00:01:26,781",
      "start_seconds": 81.434,
      "end_seconds": 86.781,
      "text": "And after 20-30 minutes, you will have a real understanding of where you are now and where you need to move next.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_020.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start": "00:01:27,041",
      "end": "00:01:36,493",
      "start_seconds": 87.041,
      "end_seconds": 96.493,
      "text": "And then another critically important point, a mistake I constantly see, is that people open many chats and try to learn in them.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_021.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start": "00:01:36,513",
      "end": "00:01:42,723",
      "start_seconds": 96.513,
      "end_seconds": 102.723,
      "text": "But it is very important to open only one chat and learn in it.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_022.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start": "00:01:43,324",
      "end": "00:01:46,809",
      "start_seconds": 103.324,
      "end_seconds": 106.809,
      "text": "Because then this chat remembers everything about you.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_023.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start": "00:01:46,829",
      "end": "00:01:54,260",
      "start_seconds": 106.829,
      "end_seconds": 114.26,
      "text": "What mistakes you made, what you said wrong, what you've already covered, what needs to be reinforced again.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_024.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start": "00:01:54,660",
      "end": "00:02:01,450",
      "start_seconds": 114.66,
      "end_seconds": 121.45,
      "text": "And when you open new chats, this memory is not saved, and you seemingly go through the same thing again.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_025.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start": "00:02:01,700",
      "end": "00:02:05,927",
      "start_seconds": 121.7,
      "end_seconds": 125.927,
      "text": "So, we stick to one chat, one teacher.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_026.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start": "00:02:05,947",
      "end": "00:02:07,450",
      "start_seconds": 125.947,
      "end_seconds": 127.45,
      "text": "Well, now for our second step.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_027.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start": "00:02:07,490",
      "end": "00:02:12,698",
      "start_seconds": 127.49,
      "end_seconds": 132.698,
      "text": "Now we will create with you that very teacher who will teach us.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_028.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start": "00:02:13,279",
      "end": "00:02:17,346",
      "start_seconds": 133.279,
      "end_seconds": 137.346,
      "text": "And let's read this prompt, well, you can copy it later.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_029.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start": "00:02:17,326",
      "end": "00:02:21,831",
      "start_seconds": 137.326,
      "end_seconds": 141.831,
      "text": "I am learning English, my level is A1, here you can insert your level.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_030.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start": "00:02:22,351",
      "end": "00:02:29,419",
      "start_seconds": 142.351,
      "end_seconds": 149.419,
      "text": "Teach me like a patient teacher, from simple to complex, in small steps, with constant repetition, without overload.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_031.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start": "00:02:29,999",
      "end": "00:02:43,333",
      "start_seconds": 149.999,
      "end_seconds": 163.333,
      "text": "Work with me in one chat, remember my typical mistakes, return to them later, first explain, then give practice, then repeat, speak simply and clearly.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_032.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start": "00:02:43,313",
      "end": "00:02:54,668",
      "start_seconds": 163.313,
      "end_seconds": 174.668,
      "text": "And with this step, you do a very important thing: you don't just open another random chat, you create your own constant, stable teacher.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_033.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start": "00:02:54,688",
      "end": "00:03:02,098",
      "start_seconds": 174.688,
      "end_seconds": 182.098,
      "text": "So, you've already created your teacher, you've given him a goal, now we're going to practice.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_034.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start": "00:03:02,118",
      "end": "00:03:08,146",
      "start_seconds": 182.118,
      "end_seconds": 188.146,
      "text": "The next step is to get some ready-made phrases from him that match our level.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_035.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start": "00:03:08,386",
      "end": "00:03:09,608",
      "start_seconds": 188.386,
      "end_seconds": 189.608,
      "text": "What do we write to him?",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_036.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start": "00:03:10,769",
      "end": "00:03:16,458",
      "start_seconds": 190.769,
      "end_seconds": 196.458,
      "text": "Give me 10 very simple English phrases for A1 level on the topic of introductions, without grammatical explanations.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_037.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start": "00:03:17,039",
      "end": "00:03:24,370",
      "start_seconds": 197.039,
      "end_seconds": 204.37,
      "text": "Here you can change both the level and the topic for which you want to receive these phrases, but, overall, I think the logic is clear.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_038.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start": "00:03:24,791",
      "end": "00:03:29,718",
      "start_seconds": 204.791,
      "end_seconds": 209.718,
      "text": "And look, if he sends us, I'll add a screenshot here, he sends it directly.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_039.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start": "00:03:29,938",
      "end": "00:03:33,604",
      "start_seconds": 209.938,
      "end_seconds": 213.604,
      "text": "Okay, here are 10 very simple phrases for A1 level on the topic of introductions.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_040.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start": "00:03:34,715",
      "end": "00:03:39,420",
      "start_seconds": 214.715,
      "end_seconds": 219.42,
      "text": "And there's a list there, hello, hi, my name is Anna, and so on.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_041.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start": "00:03:39,440",
      "end": "00:03:46,227",
      "start_seconds": 219.44,
      "end_seconds": 226.227,
      "text": "In principle, he did his job, he sent you not just words, but whole ready-made phrases like that.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_042.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start": "00:03:46,247",
      "end": "00:03:54,075",
      "start_seconds": 226.247,
      "end_seconds": 234.075,
      "text": "And I think you should already know that English should be learned not with individual words, but with ready-made language chunks.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_043.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start": "00:03:54,515",
      "end": "00:03:58,339",
      "start_seconds": 234.515,
      "end_seconds": 238.339,
      "text": "The next stage for us will be listening and a prompt for listening.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_044.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start": "00:03:58,960",
      "end": "00:04:02,023",
      "start_seconds": 238.96,
      "end_seconds": 242.023,
      "text": "Read these phrases aloud slowly.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_045.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start": "00:04:02,243",
      "end": "00:04:04,165",
      "start_seconds": 242.243,
      "end_seconds": 244.165,
      "text": "And now I'll show you how it works.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_046.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start": "00:04:04,600",
      "end": "00:04:05,681",
      "start_seconds": 244.6,
      "end_seconds": 245.681,
      "text": "Listen.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_047.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start": "00:04:05,701",
      "end": "00:04:10,106",
      "start_seconds": 245.701,
      "end_seconds": 250.106,
      "text": "I will now read them clearly and slowly, so it will be easy for you to repeat.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_048.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start": "00:04:10,486",
      "end": "00:04:11,447",
      "start_seconds": 250.486,
      "end_seconds": 251.447,
      "text": "Ready?",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_049.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start": "00:04:11,467",
      "end": "00:04:11,987",
      "start_seconds": 251.467,
      "end_seconds": 251.987,
      "text": "Let's go.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_050.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start": "00:04:12,588",
      "end": "00:04:13,049",
      "start_seconds": 252.588,
      "end_seconds": 253.049,
      "text": "First.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_051.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start": "00:04:13,409",
      "end": "00:04:14,250",
      "start_seconds": 253.409,
      "end_seconds": 254.25,
      "text": "Hello.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_052.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start": "00:04:14,270",
      "end": "00:04:14,710",
      "start_seconds": 254.27,
      "end_seconds": 254.71,
      "text": "Second.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_053.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start": "00:04:14,971",
      "end": "00:04:15,351",
      "start_seconds": 254.971,
      "end_seconds": 255.351,
      "text": "Hi.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_054.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start": "00:04:15,791",
      "end": "00:04:16,232",
      "start_seconds": 255.791,
      "end_seconds": 256.232,
      "text": "Third.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_055.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start": "00:04:16,252",
      "end": "00:04:17,633",
      "start_seconds": 256.252,
      "end_seconds": 257.633,
      "text": "My name is Anna.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_056.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start": "00:04:18,034",
      "end": "00:04:18,614",
      "start_seconds": 258.034,
      "end_seconds": 258.614,
      "text": "Fourth.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_057.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start": "00:04:18,634",
      "end": "00:04:19,956",
      "start_seconds": 258.634,
      "end_seconds": 259.956,
      "text": "I am Anna.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_058.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start": "00:04:19,976",
      "end": "00:04:20,456",
      "start_seconds": 259.976,
      "end_seconds": 260.456,
      "text": "Fifth.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_059.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start": "00:04:20,816",
      "end": "00:04:21,617",
      "start_seconds": 260.816,
      "end_seconds": 261.617,
      "text": "What is your name?",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_060.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start": "00:04:22,078",
      "end": "00:04:22,879",
      "start_seconds": 262.078,
      "end_seconds": 262.879,
      "text": "Sixth.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_061.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start": "00:04:22,899",
      "end": "00:04:24,180",
      "start_seconds": 262.899,
      "end_seconds": 264.18,
      "text": "Nice to meet you.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_062.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start": "00:04:24,200",
      "end": "00:04:24,580",
      "start_seconds": 264.2,
      "end_seconds": 264.58,
      "text": "Seventh.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_063.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start": "00:04:24,901",
      "end": "00:04:26,362",
      "start_seconds": 264.901,
      "end_seconds": 266.362,
      "text": "I am from Ukraine.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_064.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start": "00:04:26,382",
      "end": "00:04:26,843",
      "start_seconds": 266.382,
      "end_seconds": 266.843,
      "text": "Eighth.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_065.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start": "00:04:27,203",
      "end": "00:04:28,404",
      "start_seconds": 267.203,
      "end_seconds": 268.404,
      "text": "Where are you from?",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_066.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start": "00:04:28,424",
      "end": "00:04:29,265",
      "start_seconds": 268.424,
      "end_seconds": 269.265,
      "text": "Ninth.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_067.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start": "00:04:29,285",
      "end": "00:04:30,346",
      "start_seconds": 269.285,
      "end_seconds": 270.346,
      "text": "How are you?",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_068.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start": "00:04:30,366",
      "end": "00:04:30,947",
      "start_seconds": 270.366,
      "end_seconds": 270.947,
      "text": "Tenth.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_069.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start": "00:04:30,967",
      "end": "00:04:32,228",
      "start_seconds": 270.967,
      "end_seconds": 272.228,
      "text": "I am fine.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_070.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start": "00:04:32,208",
      "end": "00:04:36,143",
      "start_seconds": 272.208,
      "end_seconds": 276.143,
      "text": "I'll repeat as many times as needed, if you need it, just say and we'll do more.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_071.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start": "00:04:36,663",
      "end": "00:04:37,885",
      "start_seconds": 276.663,
      "end_seconds": 277.885,
      "text": "Like this.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_072.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start": "00:04:37,905",
      "end": "00:04:39,066",
      "start_seconds": 277.905,
      "end_seconds": 279.066,
      "text": "Look, what's important here.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_073.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start": "00:04:39,126",
      "end": "00:04:40,788",
      "start_seconds": 279.126,
      "end_seconds": 280.788,
      "text": "You can listen to this more than once.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_074.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start": "00:04:40,808",
      "end": "00:04:43,452",
      "start_seconds": 280.808,
      "end_seconds": 283.452,
      "text": "Rather, I really advise you to listen to this more than once.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_075.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start": "00:04:43,812",
      "end": "00:04:44,253",
      "start_seconds": 283.812,
      "end_seconds": 284.253,
      "text": "For what?",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_076.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start": "00:04:44,273",
      "end": "00:04:53,425",
      "start_seconds": 284.273,
      "end_seconds": 293.425,
      "text": "So that you will fix it in your head, your brain will process it better and will be able to recognize it later in real language, in real live language.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_077.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start": "00:04:53,886",
      "end": "00:04:59,794",
      "start_seconds": 293.886,
      "end_seconds": 299.794,
      "text": "And it will also be able to then suggest options for these phrases when you speak English yourself.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_078.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start": "00:04:59,874",
      "end": "00:05:01,856",
      "start_seconds": 299.874,
      "end_seconds": 301.856,
      "text": "So listen as much as possible.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_079.wav"
    },
