      "index": 83,
      "start": "00:05:21,652",
      "end": "00:05:32,587",
      "start_seconds": 321.652,
      "end_seconds": 332.587,
      "text": "That is, we will once again polish those phrases and expressions that you have already read and heard just now, and what will be our prompt for this.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_083.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start": "00:05:32,888",
      "end": "00:05:33,929",
      "start_seconds": 332.888,
      "end_seconds": 333.929,
      "text": "Look.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_084.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start": "00:05:33,949",
      "end": "00:05:37,033",
      "start_seconds": 333.949,
      "end_seconds": 337.033,
      "text": "Let's create a monologue, a story, a text for reading.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_085.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start": "00:05:37,354",
      "end": "00:05:40,278",
      "start_seconds": 337.354,
      "end_seconds": 340.278,
      "text": "Of six sentences for A1 level with these phrases.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_086.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start": "00:05:40,739",
      "end": "00:05:50,292",
      "start_seconds": 340.739,
      "end_seconds": 350.292,
      "text": "It should sound like live language, one paragraph, sentences are logically connected, without a list and without separate phrases, so that it can be said in one breath.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_087.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start": "00:05:50,272",
      "end": "00:05:54,499",
      "start_seconds": 350.272,
      "end_seconds": 354.499,
      "text": "And now I'll show you what it created for me.",
