    {
      "index": 89,
      "start": "00:05:54,519",
      "end": "00:05:57,083",
      "start_seconds": 354.519,
      "end_seconds": 357.083,
      "text": "Here I'm adding a screenshot of its answer.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_089.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start": "00:05:57,443",
      "end": "00:05:58,465",
      "start_seconds": 357.443,
      "end_seconds": 358.465,
      "text": "And what to do with this?",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_090.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start": "00:05:58,865",
      "end": "00:06:01,489",
      "start_seconds": 358.865,
      "end_seconds": 361.489,
      "text": "You can read this aloud to yourself.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_091.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start": "00:06:02,811",
      "end": "00:06:04,414",
      "start_seconds": 362.811,
      "end_seconds": 364.414,
      "text": "Even more than once.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_092.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start": "00:06:04,434",
      "end": "00:06:10,183",
      "start_seconds": 364.434,
      "end_seconds": 370.183,
      "text": "You can ask it to voice it again through that button I already showed you.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_093.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start": "00:06:10,563",
      "end": "00:06:11,445",
      "start_seconds": 370.563,
      "end_seconds": 371.445,
      "text": "And what's important here?",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_094.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start": "00:06:11,545",
      "end": "00:06:17,494",
      "start_seconds": 371.545,
      "end_seconds": 377.494,
      "text": "That your brain perceives what it has heard somewhere before and it starts to recall it.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_095.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start": "00:06:17,474",
      "end": "00:06:44,898",
      "start_seconds": 377.474,
      "end_seconds": 404.898,
      "text": "And at this moment you are really learning And now we will move on to grammar But I will not ask it now to write down the rules of use for me I will ask it to simply explain it to me And look what we can write to it Explain very simply what I am means without grammatical terms and complex explanations Look what it answers me.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_096.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start": "00:06:45,398",
      "end": "00:06:48,222",
      "start_seconds": 405.398,
      "end_seconds": 408.222,
      "text": "I am, I am. It's what you say about yourself.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_097.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start": "00:06:48,282",
      "end": "00:06:53,969",
      "start_seconds": 408.282,
      "end_seconds": 413.969,
      "text": "When you want to say who you are, what you are like, how you feel, you start with I am.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_098.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start": "00:06:53,989",
      "end": "00:06:55,430",
      "start_seconds": 413.989,
      "end_seconds": 415.43,
      "text": "And real-life examples follow.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_099.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start": "00:06:55,550",
      "end": "00:06:56,952",
      "start_seconds": 415.55,
      "end_seconds": 416.952,
      "text": "In my opinion, the explanation is great.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_100.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start": "00:06:56,972",
      "end": "00:07:00,656",
      "start_seconds": 416.972,
      "end_seconds": 420.656,
      "text": "There are no complex terms, no specific rules, no tenses here.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_101.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start": "00:07:01,157",
      "end": "00:07:06,263",
      "start_seconds": 421.157,
      "end_seconds": 426.263,
      "text": "It's simply logical, clear, and just wonderful at the beginning.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_102.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start": "00:07:06,243",
      "end": "00:07:10,630",
      "start_seconds": 426.243,
      "end_seconds": 430.63,
      "text": "Of course, if it's a different level, it will be a bit more complicated.",
      "audio_path": "audio/how_en_103.wav"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start": "00:07:10,730",
      "end": "00:07:14,336",
      "start_seconds": 430.73,
      "end_seconds": 434.336,
      "text": "You'll see all of this in the prompts, but for now, the logic is as follows.",
